<plot>A documentary giving video game fans a behind-the-scenes look at the making the 1997 Westwood interactive game "Guardians of Destiny". Includes interviews with the cast and crew, who relate some of their experiences with making the filmed portions of the game, as well as giving their views on all the work that went into it.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?573907</url></doc>
